            <h4 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">REGISTRATION</h4>
            <br>
            <h6 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">SIGN UP (Travelers)</h6>
            <p class="center" style="font-size:2vmin">Click the picture on the side for more, it is recommended to use PC</p>
            <ol>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you are the first user, click "SIGN UP" on the blue button on the bottom right
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                There are two options "TRAVELER" and "LOKADiSE", if you are a traveler, click "TRAVELER"
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You are asked to fill in your data such as name, email and password. Click the data column to bring up the keyboard.            
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                When the keyboard appears, click on the keyboard and an illustration of your data will appear.            
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                After that, click "SIGN UP".
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
