            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you have entered "Home", you will see a prototype display features.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You can scroll, then swipe left and right on the travel menu options (in the Tanjung Kelayang column) or click the next and previous symbols to see other travel options.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you are interested in traveling, click on the existing tourist destination you want to go, here, I design at Tanjung Kelayang. Click "Tanjung Kelayang" for more.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You will be shown in detail the Tanjung Kelayang tourist destination. There are details about location, itinerary, include & exclude, Terms & Conditions, Do's & Dont's, and personal equipment list.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you are interested, you can see the schedule available on the Trip Book, fill in the number of travelers, then click "BOOK NOW" for more.
            </li>
          </ol>
